EN: This museum displays a large number of antiques.

ZH:爷爷留下了一些古董给我。

EN: Grandpa left some antiques for me.

ZH:这个房间里放着很多古董。

EN: There are many antiques in this room.

ZH:他对收集古董很感兴趣。

EN: He is very interested in collecting antiques.

ZH:你知道哪里可以买到一些古董吗？

EN: Do you know where I can buy some antiques?

ZH:这家店里卖的都是古董。

EN: This store sells only antiques.

ZH:她的家里挂满了古董。

EN: Her house is full of antiques.

ZH:他们家族传承了很多珍贵的古董。

EN: Their family has inherited many precious antiques.

ZH:这是一个用古董装饰的博物馆。

EN: This is a museum decorated with antiques.

ZH:这块古董有着悠久的历史。

EN: This antique has a long history.

ZH:这把古董枪据说是一位将军的遗物。

EN: This antique gun is said to be a relic of a general.

ZH:古董市场上有很多值得收藏的物品。

